snippet.textDisplay: Usually Amber Heard is all over rumors that she has been fired with planted stories like ScreenGeek's "Amber Heard Unlikely To Lose Aquaman 2 Role or L'Oreal Contract". I don't think that she would directly contradict the story, if she knew that she had been fired...but she might, just to try to save face. I'm not breaking open the bubbly just yet, but I'm a LOT happier than I was before this news broke!
